{"tid":478143,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"難以置信，G.E.M.出左新廣東歌都無人講！？","createTime":"2017-11-23T18:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T12:36:14.000Z","uid":555,"like":9,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cf297ea6570ad21160890c06ae59f31e00f4072f","tid":478143,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T18:08:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KV2aigTQBAE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKV2aigTQBAE&d=jOq8K1o5peKA5FJpE7s9s5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=962a6cfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KV2aigTQBAE</a><br />\nVictoria<br />\n主唱：G.E.M.鄧紫棋<br />\n曲：G.E.M.鄧紫棋<br />\n詞：G.E.M.鄧紫棋／王祖藍／陳國濱／林洛民 <br />\n編曲:王雙駿<br />\n監製:王雙駿<br />\n<br />\n凝望對岸燈火線<br />\n童年望到如今不厭 <br />\n流連球場內媽媽有些怨言<br />\n卻是那最熟悉聲線<br />\n<br />\n常回味那蛋撻的脆<br />\n人情味也屬於這裡<br />\n誰曾離別天星下再相聚<br />\n你共我已成長幾歲<br />\n<br />\n看遍風雨和繁花<br />\n共灌溉七百萬童話<br />\nVictoria Victoria<br />\n你的我的  這一個家<br />\n<br />\n重讀幼嫩的筆記<br />\n記載著還在努力的希冀<br />\n時代門外多少摯真憶記<br />\n那是有過夢想的你<br />\n<br />\n看遍風雨和繁花<br />\n共灌溉七百萬童話<br />\nVictoria Victoria<br />\n你的我的  這一個家<br />\n<br />\n即使幾多驚濤駭浪<br />\n即使都少不免相撞<br />\n可否牽手一同泊岸<br />\n這景致誰亦嚮往<br />\n<br />\n無論幾多次迷路不怕<br />\n沿著港灣會望見煙花<br />\n<br />\n世界千百樣圖畫<br />\n但你我也只渴望回家<br />\nVictoria Victoria<br />\n你的我的  這一個家<br />\n<br />\n冷暖起跌像浮沙<br />\n用愛種七百萬童話<br />\nVictoria Victoria<br />\n你的我的  這一個家"},{"pid":"3daf9aace7d1fce87211161f4b11b0151960cf01","tid":478143,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T18:09:06.000Z","msg":"娛樂台有一個post 驚有人睇唔到 音樂台開多個"},{"pid":"ae5bb658814cd5086da46de99962a4562e434428","tid":478143,"uid":51978,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T18:10:09.000Z","msg":"好難聽啊屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cdb3b78b9b536adfba2a1905ed8c3893e389151","tid":478143,"uid":9736,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-