\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.minus.com%2FibvDtwkmyklAlE.gif&h=5e69775b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我是歌手<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>亞軍</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-a.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-frc3/l/t31.0-8/1921040_374359186038934_438503127_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-a.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fhphotos-frc3%2Fl%2Ft31.0-8%2F1921040_374359186038934_438503127_o.jpg&h=4271d459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20130907075951/evchk/images/d/dd/1378272004_939b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic2.wikia.nocookie.net%2F__cb20130907075951%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fd%2Fdd%2F1378272004_939b.jpg&h=04a682f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n撐CY，有前途！689，有出路！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/31M0P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2F31M0P.jpg&h=fce46610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以CY做榜樣，拆牆做開放式廚房，用埋煤氣爐都冇問題啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vignette3.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/b/b6/10155865_10152773287226038_7883309153044613813_n.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20140622090433\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette3.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fb%2Fb6%2F10155865_10152773287226038_7883309153044613813_n.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20140622090433&h=18943486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你個世界都真係幾大喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/88/Gemkoreastarstarlove.JPG/revision/latest?cb=20140523064837\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette2.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F8%2F88%2FGemkoreastarstarlove.JPG%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20140523064837&h=5eca1057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都敏俊？邊撚度俊呀？依家冇人識你呀！邊撚度俊呀？屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/large/68f631fagw1ehj8vsfvo7j20z64cnnpd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww3.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F68f631fagw1ehj8vsfvo7j20z64cnnpd.jpg&h=0c98aae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n既然係宇宙天后，當然要有元首級嘅保護啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.na.cx/F416w5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2FF416w5.png&h=383d8ebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾威水呀！宇宙天后終於入咗<strong>杜麗莎夫人蠟像館啦</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.na.cx/bT0kHD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2FbT0kHD.png&h=7fbe8fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際天后幾親民呀！拎到獎梗係第一時間見fans啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慶功宴？Who fucking cares? </div><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.na.cx/1623y7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2F1623y7.png&h=e6ad1b56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇下G.E.M.幾受歡迎，一開演唱會就份份報紙都報啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.na.cx/ofOw2y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2FofOw2y.png&h=eb8d8fb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有G.E.M.個logo o係上面呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />280蚊梗係物超所值啦！淘寶貨點比得上？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5mbdiwh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5mbdiwh.png&h=1649f548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孝女G.E.M.幾有心機呀，特登寫張紙賀父親節同媽媽生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/d19098677e330erwl2f77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fd19098677e330erwl2f77.jpg&h=f7066558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天后出現了！但是和CY一樣，都係會告人誹謗的&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20130906/large/1378439842_7f2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20130906%2Flarge%2F1378439842_7f2b.jpg&h=d4041066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20130906/large/1378439843_d1a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20130906%2Flarge%2F1378439843_d1a0.jpg&h=efda66ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李思嫣，陳淨心都撐！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e85wc0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe85wc0.png&h=ba541dd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲唔黎支持新一代宇宙小天后？微博關注差唔多<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>二千萬</strong></span>啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.na.cx/1424kS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2F1424kS.png&h=3edd5a06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n禮拜六啦！各位去咗政總支持罷課學生未呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7814k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7814k.png&h=5319a2eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HL8oCJbqgNI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHL8oCJbqgNI&d=jOq8K1o5peKA5FJpE7s9s5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=073f9609\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HL8oCJbqgNI</a><br />\n宇宙G.E.M.不知幾勁，連Katy Perry都要坐時光機抄佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww2.sinaimg.cn/wap720/6a2e8a18gw1exi49ffcdfj20jp0hxn1z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww2.sinaimg.cn%2Fwap720%2F6a2e8a18gw1exi49ffcdfj20jp0hxn1z.jpg&h=0eb01e4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RHFyDrSPBZc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRHFyDrSPBZc&d=jOq8K1o5peKA5FJpE7s9s5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=3bbb400c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RHFyDrSPBZc</a><br />\nG.E.M.嘅新碟幾勁，已經變成Apple產品啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br